{
  "texts": [
    "We evaluated four relative threshold types from (Kamradt, 2024):",
    "• Percentile: The nth percentile of the linear interpolation of the distance array.",
    "We tested [10, 30, 50, 70, 90].",
    "• Standard deviation: The mean of the linear interpolation plus a fraction of the standard deviation.",
    "We tested [1, 1.5, 2, 2.5, 3]."
  ]
}